KT_Project1 README

Report: knwtech_report2.pdf

How to compile it:

- Global Edit Distance (GED)

Under the porject1 folder:

1. g++ gobal_editdistance.cpp

2. ./a.out

3. Change query and tweet document, please revise these two lines:

#define QUERY_FILE "query1K-1grams.txt"
#define TWEET_FILE "tweetResult3K.1gram.txt"


- Local Edit Distance (LED)

Under the porject1 folder:

1. g++ local_editdistance.cpp

2. ./a.out

3. Change query and tweet document, please revise these two lines:

#define QUERY_FILE "queries.1K.txt"
#define TWEET_FILE "tweets.3K.noNum.txt"



